                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="421492" author="simmonsja" created="Thu, 18 Jul 2024 20:51:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Moving to 2.15 LTS seems to make this problem a lot less. We can close this ticket.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="406203" author="simmonsja" created="Mon, 4 Mar 2024 19:47:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;All the settings are in sync &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/images/icons/emoticons/sad.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="405859" author="adilger" created="Thu, 29 Feb 2024 23:33:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Is this client mounting multiple Lustre filesystems?  Are the timeouts on this client the same on all of the filesystems?  This is one of the common issues when a client is being evicted regularly after mounting multiple filesystems with different timeouts.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Not sure about the LNet error.  If TCP, is &lt;tt&gt;conns_per_peer&lt;/tt&gt; set the same on the client and servers?  &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
